			<p>
				The EclipseLink SDO component delivers the reference
				implementation of the Service Data Objects (SDO) 2.1.1.
				The EclipseLink SDO implementation enables Java
				developer to efficiently build and use data object
				models that can be incorporated into service
				architectures.
			</p>
		</description>
